data.description: *** MOTIVATED SELLER***Need a large home with views?  This is the place for you.  This 2,560 sq. ft. home boasts 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, 2 Living Rooms,  Dining Room, Open Kitchen, Ample Closet space in almost every room, an extra room for an office, and a beautiful green lawn with views of the Wind River Mtns.  Come take a look today!
data.whatILove: We love the open concept floor plan as well as the fact that the master bedroom seems more private since it is on the opposite end of the home. The mountain views are stunning and it has its own well so you can have a lawn. Its on a corner lots so lots of room to move around or even build a shop.
